<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I just cannot get over that Gwen died. Im so angry,<br /> I can't read anymore. Hadn't Royce lost enough? I suppose I'm so upset because it mirrors my own life and all the losses. I can't take one more loss and so I have given up on this series. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
